name: Circuit #001 Monaco GP
description:
The Circuit de Monaco has been a street circuit since 1929 and has held the Formula 1 Grand Prix annually since 1950.

Along with the 24 Hours of Le Mans and Indianapolis 500, it is one of the Triple Crowns of Motorsport - an unofficial achievement for those who have won all three races.

Ayrton Senna (1960-1994) still holds the record for most victories in Monaco as a driver (6), and Mclaren as a builder (15).


-------
